{"tid":1680922,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先去左大家樂食飯","createTime":"2019-10-29T06:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T14:19:00.000Z","uid":35063,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"134c2445b7be038bdad9a11c6d151bce7ce28e5e","tid":1680922,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"對唔住，小弟做野要四圍去，今日趕時間無得揀唯有去大家樂食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一入到去法國拍哂烏蠅，食飯時間都得幾個廢中廢佬加埋都唔知有無10個<br />\n我地兩條友叫左一個咖哩牛腩一咖喱魚柳<br />\n跟住住佢問我地要唔要檸樂<br />\n<br />\n免費既<br />\n<br />\n個下我呆一呆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗都已經唔記得大家樂上次咖喱飯包野飲係幾多咸風年前既事，仲要係檸樂#peanut#<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證明我地既黃色經濟圈係行之有效，希望大家繼續持之以恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jcFUvM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jcFUvM.png&h=40b64287&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84fe7e6057977b21e2d98ff5ae63813e296b47e5","tid":1680922,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:05:03.000Z","msg":"$1交稅攬炒機械人小測成績表已出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679773</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30427a43d8e67ca4cebecbb0025e5cc1160b543","tid":1680922,"uid":64632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"牙k去到咁遠開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d01242f4aaf59c6d3091984414397fa8bee5cb9","tid":1680922,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8YNzxz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8YNzxz.gif&h=f70efd53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vFj95V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-s